Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Blue Steel
Rare Special Items.lore: This is the malbec of weapon design - Booth, Arms Dealer

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Boreal Forest
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a forest camouflage hydrographic.
Rare Special Items.lore: The woods can be a dangerous place... never travel alone

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Safari Mesh
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using mesh fencing and cardboard cutouts as stencils.
Rare Special Items.lore: A predator is a predator, no matter the environment

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Crimson Web
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a spider web-patterned hydrographic over a red base coat and finished with a semi-gloss topcoat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Be careful where you walk, you never know where the web is spread

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Forest DDPAT
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a Digital Disruptive Pattern (DDPAT) hydrographic.
Rare Special Items.lore: By the time you're close enough to notice the pixels it's already too late

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Fade
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted by airbrushing transparent paints that fade together over a chrome base coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: This isn't just a weapon, it's a conversation piece - Imogen, Arms Dealer In Training

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Slaughter
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted in a zebra-stripe pattern with aluminum and chrome paints with various reflectivities, and has then been covered with a tomato red candy coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Valeria doesn't pay Javier to ask questions... she pays him to pry out answers

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Urban Masked
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using a tangle of masking tape as a stencil.
Rare Special Items.lore: True power is demonstrated with subtle application

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Case Hardened
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been color case-hardened through the application of wood charcoal at high temperatures.
Rare Special Items.lore: A little color never hurt anyone

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Stained
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been given a forced patina using lemon and mustard dripped onto the surface.
Rare Special Items.lore: If you think it's messy now, wait until you see it under a blacklight

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Scorched
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted in a sun-dappled pattern.
Rare Special Items.lore: The Phoenix is not a symbol of destruction... it's a symbol of rebirth - Valeria Jenner, Revolutionary

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Classic Knife | Night Stripe
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted with a tape mask pattern in a night ops color scheme.

Covert Skins.name: AWP | Wildfire
Covert Skins.desc: The Operation Wildfire logo has been hand painted over a black and red base.
Covert Skins.lore: The nail that sticks out gets the hammer

Covert Skins.name: FAMAS | Commemoration
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted gold and features various details celebrating 20 years of Counter-Strike.

Classified Skins.name: MP9 | Hydra
Classified Skins.desc: A custom paint job referencing Operation Hydra, CS:GO's 8th Operation, has been applied.

Classified Skins.name: AUG | Death by Puppy
Classified Skins.desc: A multicolored Pop Dog pattern has been applied.

Classified Skins.name: P90 | Nostalgia
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a CT from the main menu of the original Counter-Strike.
Classified Skins.lore: Minutes to install but a lifetime to master

Restricted Skins.name: M249 | Aztec
Restricted Skins.desc: Excavated from Aztec ruins, parts of this M249 have rusted and been covered in moss.

Restricted Skins.name: Five-SeveN | Buddy
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with camo patterns and a CT beneath the rear sight.

Restricted Skins.name: P250 | Inferno
Restricted Skins.desc: A custom paint job which reflects the ethos of de_inferno has been applied.

Restricted Skins.name: UMP-45 | Plastique
Restricted Skins.desc: A custom paint job of wires, a green circuit board, and a number pad has been applied.

Restricted Skins.name: MP5-SD | Agent
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted in FBI blue and finished with yellow accents.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Glock-18 | Sacrifice
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: This custom paint job pays homage to olofmeister's burning defuse on Overpass at ESL One Cologne 2014.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: "The defuse is coming in—he's still going!"

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Tec-9 | Flash Out
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to resemble a flashbang grenade.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: FAMAS | Decommissioned
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: This custom paint job is inspired by elements found on de_nuke from Counter-Strike 1.6.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: If found please return to Cedar Creek Nuclear Power Plant

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MAC-10 | Classic Crate
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been hand painted to resemble the green metal crates originally found on de_dust2.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: SCAR-20 | Assault
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: The logo of a research facility has been hand painted in white over a blue base.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MAG-7 | Popdog
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to resemble a train car with Pop Dog painted on the side.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Dual Berettas | Elite 1.6
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: ELITE has been stamped on the side of these classic Dual Berettas.
